@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BackofficeOperator
participant ":System" as System

activate BackofficeOperator

BackofficeOperator -> System : Requests to edit a customer's collaborator

activate System
System --> BackofficeOperator : Requests customer, collaborator and new contact data
deactivate System

BackofficeOperator -> System : Provides customer, collaborator, new email and new phone number

activate System
System --> System : Check if Backoffice Operator is authorized
System --> System : Validate customer
System --> System : Validate collaborator
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to customer
System --> System : Validate new email
System --> System : Check email uniqueness
System --> System : Validate new phone number
System --> System : Ensure only email and phone number are changed

alt update data is valid
    System --> System : Update collaborator contact information
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Collaborator updated successfully
else update data is invalid
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate BackofficeOperator

@enduml